queries.sql: SELECT tbl_pengguna.*, tbl_umkm.id as id_umkm, tbl_umkm.nama as nama_umkm, tbl_umkm.deskripsi, tbl_umkm.foto as foto_umkm, tbl_umkm.alamat as alamat_umkm, tbl_umkm.city_id, tbl_city.province_id FROM tbl_pengguna left join tbl_umkm on tbl_umkm.id_pengguna = tbl_pengguna.id left join tbl_city on tbl_umkm.city_id = tbl_city.city_id where tbl_pengguna.id = '14'

SELECT DISTINCT tbl_menu.id_menu_title, tbl_menu_title.title FROM `tbl_menu` JOIN tbl_menu_title ON tbl_menu_title.id=tbl_menu.id_menu_title WHERE role='RESELLER' AND tbl_menu.status='ACTIVE' ORDER BY tbl_menu_title.urutan ASC;
SELECT tbl_menu.* FROM tbl_menu WHERE tbl_menu.status = 'ACTIVE' AND tbl_menu.id_menu_title = '3' AND tbl_menu.role = 'RESELLER' ORDER BY tbl_menu.urutan ASC

SELECT tbl_menu.* FROM tbl_menu WHERE tbl_menu.status = 'ACTIVE' AND tbl_menu.id_menu_title = '5' AND tbl_menu.role = 'RESELLER' ORDER BY tbl_menu.urutan ASC
